s of balloon fight with a steerable and intuitive control.\n\nPlay to relax and escape, or complete all missions and 100% the game. ", "short_description": "Take to the skies in a hot air balloon and explore a vast beautiful landscape."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "http://www.vector3up.co.uk/ballooning-adventures-privacy-policy.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "http://www.vector3up.co.uk/ballooning-adventures-terms-of-service.html", "publisher_name": "Vector3Up", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://www.vector3up.co.uk/ballooningadventures.html", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ACTION", "ADVENTURE", "EXPLORATION"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "653681422448125"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "170086434961478"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "170086434961478"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1616447880, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "170086434961478"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "3822487431176466", "version": "1.1.2"}, "id": "846569332864513", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus_keys_only": false, "primary_binaries": {"nodes": [{"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "3700318683393342", "is_con